div.forgot-form-container(tg-forgot-password)
    p.forgot-text
        strong(translate) Oops, did you forget your password? <br/>
        strong(translate) Enter your username or email to get a new one

    form(ng-submit="ctrl.submit()")
        fieldset
            input(type="text", name="username", ng-model="data.username", data-required="true",
                  placeholder="{{'Username or email' | translate}}")
        fieldset
            button.button-gray.submit-button.button-forgot(type="submit", title="{{'Reset Password' | translate}}", translate) Reset Password

        a(href="", title="Login", tg-nav="login", translate) Nah, take me back. I think I remember it.
